{
  "description": "DB2/Snowflake/SQLite hybrid with range_unbounded_to_current window default, double-quoted identifiers with upper-fold, LIMIT/OFFSET row limiting, || concat, cast_as syntax, and set-op default ALL with group_by accepting select aliases.",
  "divergence_level": "moderate",
