  "name": "db2_snowflake_sqlite_rangefold",
  "notes": "Hybrid fusing DB2's OUTER JOIN verbosity, MOD keyword, VALUE function alias, and upper-fold with Snowflake's ILIKE support, group-by-alias, and select-resolves-through-group-by, plus SQLite's LIMIT/OFFSET and IFNULL. The headline differentiator is range_unbounded_to_current window frame default (not used by any prior slot), combined with explicit OUTER JOIN keywords and required semicolons. Conflicts with prior slots on window frame default (vs rows_unbounded_to_current in slot 8, rows_unbounded_to_unbounded in slot 11), identifier quoting (double vs backtick/bracket), and set-op default.",
